title: Open Tues 6:30-7pm.Spacious Nob Hill 2BR,Bay Windows(1525 Jackson#3)
posting_body: ['2nd', 'Floor 2BR/1BA', '* $3,095/month annual lease', '* Ornamental fireplace', '*', 'Available:', 'Now', 'OPEN HOUSE: Tuesday(8/2) 6:30pm-7pm', 'ADDRESS: 1525 Jackson Street #3', 'Second floor 2BR/1BA apartment on Jackson Street in Nob Hill neighborhood on the border with Cow Hollow.', 'Floors are hardwood except in kitchen and bath.', 'Bedrooms are at the front of the apartment, facing the street.', 'They both have bay windows.', 'One bedroom has an ornamental fireplace and built-in shelving; it has a large closet near the entrance to the apartment.', 'The other bedroom has a standard closet.', 'Living room is behind one of the bedrooms, has a credenza, and provides access to the kitchen.', 'Kitchen includes a gas stove.', 'Bath has shower-over-tub', 'Building is on Jackson at Polk.', "It's less than a block to the center of Polk Street's shopping and dining district's many offerings.", 'Walk Score is 99.', 'Transit Score is 86.', "Bus lines 1, 10, 12, 19, 27, 47, 49 and shuttles on Van Ness Avenue are all within a few blocks' walking distance.", "Tenant pays a one-time broker's fee.", 'Everest Mwamba', 'DRE# 01717299', 'Kenney & Everest Real Estate', 'DRE# 01984640', 'show contact info', 'office', 'Apply at: <URL>', 'Leasing and Real Estate: Our Family Business for Over 100 Years.', 'This unit is a rental unit subject to the San Francisco Rent Ordinance, which limits evictions without just cause, and which states that any waiver by a tenant of their rights under the Rent Ordinance is void as contrary to public policy.']
